Mandisi Dyantis: For one night, award winning jazz vocalist and trumpeter Mandisi Dyantyis brings patrons a feel of his debut album, Somandla. Details: The performance takes place on December 6 at the Untitled Basement , 7 Reserve Street, Braamfontein.
